                                                ASM International NV - ADR
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            








                                            
	ASM International NV operates in the Special industry machinery sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares ASM International NV with three other
	
			companies in this sector in the United States:
		
	Veeco Instruments Inc.
	
		(2016
	sales of $332.45 million
		of which 41%
		was Lighting, Display & Power Electronics),
	
	Brooks Automation, Inc.
	
		($560.32 million
		of which 81%
		was Brooks Semiconductor Solutions Group), and
	
	Manitex International Inc
	
		($288.96 million
		of which 60%
		was Lifting Equipment).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	ASM International NV reported sales of $659.95 million
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
			a
			
			decrease of 10.6%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were $738.56 million.
	
		Contributing to the drop in overall sales was the 10.6% decline
		in Front-End, from $738.56 million to $659.95 million.
		.
		
					However, these declines were partially offset by the increase in sales of
					Back-End (up 10.8% to $1.84 billion)
				
			.
		

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 




















                             


 


 





                         

