Structure bills of material for effective use by Engineering and Manufacturing.
	 

Perform product tolerance studies, make engineering computations and write specifications as required by engineers or supervisor.

 

Assist in ensuring that corporate design standards are maintained and monitored.
	 

Write and incorporate Engineering Change Orders.

 

Check own work and that of other designers.
	 

Estimate hours of tasks and report actual hours to manager.
	 

Determine new working methods and write procedures as necessary.
	 

As purchased parts are established, ensure they are drawn or modeled and added to the AutoCAD or Pro/ENGINEER libraries.

 

Mentor other designers on Pro/ENGINEER and ASM processes.


